---
// src/components/Tentang.astro
---

<section id="tentang" class="py-10 md:py-14 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 relative z-10">
    
    <!-- BAGIAN ATAS: DESKRIPSI SINGKAT -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
      <span class="text-[#B59449] font-semibold text-xs tracking-wider uppercase block mb-1">Tentang Kami</span>
      <h2 class="text-[#063A24] font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-3">Rumah Quran Cahaya Kebaikan</h2>
      <p class="text-[#063A24]/80 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
        Kami adalah tempat belajar mengaji Al-Quran yang dikhususkan untuk perempuan (akhwat) dan anak-anak. Di sini, kamu bisa belajar dari nol mulai dari pengenalan huruf, lancar membaca (Tahsin), sampai paham ilmu tajwid dengan suasana yang nyaman dan dibimbing langsung oleh Ustadzah.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- BAGIAN BAWAH: 3 POIN UTAMA -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 lg:gap-6">
      
      <!-- Poin 1 -->
      <div class="bg-[#FAF6EE]/40 backdrop-blur-xs p-4 rounded-xl border border-[#063A24]/10 text-center flex flex-col items-center group transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:translate-y-[-2px] hover:shadow-xs">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-[#063A24]/10 text-[#063A24] flex items-center justify-center mb-3 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-[#063A24] group-hover:text-white">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#063A24] text-base transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-[#B59449]">Khusus Akhwat</h3>
        <p class="text-[#063A24]/70 text-xs sm:text-sm mt-1 leading-relaxed">Tempat dan suasana belajar yang terjaga, jadi para tholibah bisa mengaji dengan tenang dan nyaman.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Poin 2 -->
      <div class="bg-[#FAF6EE]/40 backdrop-blur-xs p-4 rounded-xl border border-[#063A24]/10 text-center flex flex-col items-center group transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:translate-y-[-2px] hover:shadow-xs">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-[#063A24]/10 text-[#063A24] flex items-center justify-center mb-3 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-[#063A24] group-hover:text-white">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#063A24] text-base transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-[#B59449]">Belajar dari Dasar</h3>
        <p class="text-[#063A24]/70 text-xs sm:text-sm mt-1 leading-relaxed">Materi pelajaran disusun berjenjang dan jelas, cocok banget buat kamu yang mau belajar dari nol.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Poin 3 -->
      <div class="bg-[#FAF6EE]/40 backdrop-blur-xs p-4 rounded-xl border border-[#063A24]/10 text-center flex flex-col items-center group transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:translate-y-[-2px] hover:shadow-xs">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-[#063A24]/10 text-[#063A24] flex items-center justify-center mb-3 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-[#063A24] group-hover:text-white">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#063A24] text-base transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-[#B59449]">Kelas Lebih Fokus</h3>
        <p class="text-[#063A24]/70 text-xs sm:text-sm mt-1 leading-relaxed">Jumlah murid di dalam kelas dibatasi supaya proses belajar mengajar jadi lebih maksimal.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
